meta {
  name: Speaker Invitations API (Story 6.1)
}

docs {
  # Speaker Invitations API Tests - Story 6.1

  Tests for the automated speaker invitation system:
  - Send individual invitations (AC2)
  - Send bulk invitations (AC7)
  - List invitations by event (AC2)
  - Token-based response (AC2, public endpoints)
  - Expiration handling (AC9)

  ## Test Flow
  1. Create test event
  2. Send single invitation
  3. Send bulk invitations
  4. List invitations
  5. Get invitation by token (public)
  6. Respond to invitation (public)
  7. Error cases (invalid token, expired)
  8. Cleanup test event
}
